{"tid":757402,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"馬爾甘表示：我一直都想來巴塞!!!","createTime":"2018-07-26T23:06:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T12:22:21.000Z","uid":188406,"like":3,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b675ca4e202f168370063b37753294be07b282ed","tid":757402,"uid":188406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T23:06:36.000Z","msg":"馬爾甘表示：&ldquo;我一直都想來巴塞，整件事情都是我經紀人處理的。加盟巴塞是一個機會，在這裏能夠和世界上最優秀的球員們一起，來到這裏是很難的，而我會竭盡全力拿出最好的表現。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n今次合約違約金是1億8000萬歐元，看來又不是很高。相比早前兩單轉會的違約金 , 似乎有所暗示<br />\n<br />\n下一場對熱刺的熱身賽，就會有機會看到他首度上陣 !<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/27/070551_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F27%2F070551_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3cb85eae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nClick入去有完整發佈會睇   : <a href=\"https://youtu.be/11FOspvfl-I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F11FOspvfl-I&d=UAQ9pE%2FGVdgdJKmfP0crvkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=2278c923\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/11FOspvfl-I</a>"},{"pid":"6ca33ab24cf3742e4aeef25d1b43bfe1064f0783","tid":757402,"uid":188406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T00:21:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/27/082148_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F27%2F082148_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=0b66ff45&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c61c244473b960122bdc563b26aaab6dacab387","tid":757402,"uid":158755,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T01:28:31.000Z","msg":"有無Seri嘅對比圖"},{"pid":"b3c7372ee02f4bc525ff76e45f70dfc64696542e","tid":757402,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T01:29:05.000Z","msg":"馬甘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\